@EnglishLearning.API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7074

### Tum kullanicilari getir
GET {{EnglishLearning.API_HostAddress}}/api/kullanicilar

### Tek kullanici getir
GET {{EnglishLearning.API_HostAddress}}/api/kullanicilar/1

### Yeni kullanici olustur
POST {{EnglishLearning.API_HostAddress}}/api/kullanicilar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isim": "Test Kullanici",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Kullanici guncelle
PUT {{EnglishLearning.API_HostAddress}}/api/kullanicilar/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isim": "Guncel Isim",
  "email": "guncel@example.com"
}

### Kullanici sil
DELETE {{EnglishLearning.API_HostAddress}}/api/kullanicilar/1
